{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778899759165,"sessionID":"ses_1d155eb7bffekSu2beub8p2qSl","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"functions.write:21","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"Changes committed in PR #<NN>.\n\nSummary of updates for GO:0061852:\n- **New superclass added:** GO:0062137 (cargo receptor complex)\n- **Primary label updated:** \"retrograde cargo receptor complex, Golgi to ER\"\n  - The old label \"retrograde transporter complex, Golgi to ER\" is now a BROAD synonym, as requested, because it is not restricted to cargo.\n- **Definition refined:** Updated from \"Transporter complex that recognises...\" to \"Cargo receptor complex that recognizes...\"\n- Existing term tracker item preserved; new tracker item added for issue #31935.\n\nThese changes were validated with ROBOT reasoning and SPARQL QC checks.\n","filePath":"/home/runner/work/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/runner/work/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"ISSUE_COMMENTS.md","time":{"start":1778899759160,"end":1778899759164}},"id":"prt_e2eb02bdf001RkBC4LByHUYyTK","sessionID":"ses_1d155eb7bffekSu2beub8p2qSl","messageID":"msg_e2eb02a16001nrMxL5lkSuGwUH"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778899763355,"sessionID":"ses_1d155eb7bffekSu2beub8p2qSl","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"functions.write:22","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"## Summary\n\nUpdates to GO:0061852 as requested in issue #31935.\n\n### Changes made\n\n1. **New superclass (is_a):** Added `GO:0062137 ! cargo receptor complex`\n2. **Primary label change:**\n   - Old: `retrograde transporter complex, Golgi to ER`\n   - New: `retrograde cargo receptor complex, Golgi to ER`\n3. **Synonym adjustments:**\n   - Added `synonym: \"retrograde transporter complex, Golgi to ER\" BROAD []` (the old primary label)\n   - Changed existing exact synonym `retrograde transporter complex, Golgi to endoplasmic reticulum` to BROAD to be consistent with the above\n4. **Definition refinement:**\n   - Old: `Transporter complex that recognises, binds and returns...`\n   - New: `Cargo receptor complex that recognizes, binds and returns...` (also updated spelling to US English for consistency)\n5. **Term tracker:** Added `property_value: term_tracker_item \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/31935\" xsd:anyURI`\n\n### Rationale\n\nThe term GO:0061852 describes a complex that recognizes and returns ER resident proteins from Golgi to ER. It functions specifically as a cargo receptor complex, making GO:0062137 an appropriate parent. The old label \"retrograde transporter complex\" is broader than the intended scope (it could include non-cargo retrograde complexes), so it was moved to a BROAD synonym. The definition was updated to align with the new parentage and label.\n\n### Validation performed\n\n- ROBOT reasoning with ELK: PASS (no unsatisfiable classes)\n- SPARQL QC checks (equivalent classes, trailing whitespace, self-reference, synonym-label match, obsolete, namespace, duplicate synonyms, xref syntax, definition constraints): all PASS\n\n### Checklist\n\n- [x] PLAN: The issue and all its context has been analyzed, the intent is clear, and a plan for addressing it has been created\n- [x] PRE-VALIDATION: Current state of the ontology validates prior to any changes\n- [x] TERM-SEARCH: Relevant ontology terms consulted (GO:0061852 and GO:0062137)\n- [x] EDITS: Correct procedure followed (checkout via `obo-checkout.pl`, edits in `terms/`, checkin via `obo-checkin.pl`)\n- [x] RELATIONSHIPS: New `is_a` parent added; existing relationships preserved\n- [x] METADATA: Definition updated with correct source attribution (PMID:16093310, GOC:bhm); term tracker item added; no `created_by` or `creation_date` added to existing term\n- [x] AUTOMATED-VALIDATION: Ontology validates with ROBOT reason and SPARQL checks after changes\n- [x] REFERENCE-VALIDATION: Existing references preserved; no new PMIDs introduced\n- [x] CHANGES-COMMITTED: Only `src/ontology/go-edit.obo` committed\n","filePath":"/home/runner/work/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/PR_COMMENTS.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/runner/work/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/PR_COMMENTS.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"PR_COMMENTS.md","time":{"start":1778899763349,"end":1778899763353}},"id":"prt_e2eb0305a001Mq7kt7gSEU0ER3","sessionID":"ses_1d155eb7bffekSu2beub8p2qSl","messageID":"msg_e2eb02a16001nrMxL5lkSuGwUH"}}
